com.intel.fightclub.coach.test

Class ReceiverContextWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.Context
      • android.content.ContextWrapper
        • com.intel.fightclub.coach.test.ReceiverContextWrapper

  • @NotThreadSafe
public final class ReceiverContextWrapper
extends android.content.ContextWrapper
    Test context to capture all Intents broadcast through it. Captured Intents are not delivered to clients, but can be retrieved via getAndClearSentIntents().
